Big Brother Naija, BBNaija Lockdown housemate, Nengi, has said she would have sex in the reality show if she wants to despite the cameras. According to her, viewers and housemates will always talk so she does not care if she has sex on national television. She said this during a conversation with Ozo. Ozo asked: “Will you care about public if you do it (sex) on national tv?” Nengi responding said: “No I will face dem if it happens, they will still talk about other things.” The female housemate had earlier complained that condoms in the house are reducing faster. The first housemates caught having sex in this Lockdown edition were Praise and Ka3na who were not even into any serious relationships.